&lt;p&gt;As well as designing the product, I also developed the frontend. This involved building new components and revising others for the Virtual College Pattern Library. The components were hand coded in HTML and Sass with each one tested for accessibility, compatibility and performance. I coached the development team to ensure best practice was used when implementing these in the final code.&lt;/p&gt;</content:encoded></item></channel></rss>